CRYOTEK hoveed for a moment, his powerful senses taking in the scene
and then he landed on the ground, shifting to robot mode as he did so,
landing next to HYDRAS and the seemingly darker and more thickly built
version of DINOBOT.

There was a nod from LEO PRIME as he looked over HYDRAS' troops. "It
seems you have a few more troops then the reports have conveyed." LEO
said dryly as he looked pointedly at CRYOTEK and DINOBOT. if he
noticed BLACKARACHNIA or VICEGRIP there was no evidence of it.

WINGCALIBER and TORCA came over to LEO and stood next to him, much
like HYDRAS' trrops had done for him, both sides seemingly willing to
work together for the moment, but niehter willing to trust the other
completely.

"You said you would have your scientists look into the device that was
recovered from Dark Rodimus." LEO PRIME said, his optics looking
around as if searching for him. Of course he didn't see him and so he
turned his searhcing gaze back on HYDRAS, "Do you have anything new to
report before we head into the jungle?"

(TAG)

Preston
